item.title: Project 1
item.description: Benjamin Sakham Lomborg BL26735 I have choose the data from the 3 Index S&P 500, NASDAQ and Dow Jones 30 (Dow Jones 30) from 01/01/2010 to 12/31/2018. The data is in three datasets. There is 7 variables from the beginning in each dataset. Data, Open, High, Low, Close, Adj. Close and Volume. Variables Date yyyy-mm-dd Open The value the index opened in for the day High Highest value for the day Low Lowest value for the day Close The value the index closed in for the day Adj.
